    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Firmamus atque
                        concessemus nos domnus <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir
                            gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/158">Gisulfus</persName> summus
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> genti Langobardorum in <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Private_foundations" ref="#juridical_persons/3401"><rs
                                key="#Churches #Private_foundations">ęcclesia</rs> Beate
                            Sophie</orgName> quam <persName ref="#people/3453" key="#Abbots"
                            >Zacharia</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> pater noster a fundamentis edificare visus est
                        in locum qui nominatur <placeName ref="#places/3426"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">ad Pontecellum</placeName>,
                        quod fuit de quodam <name ref="Wadulfus">Vvadulfi</name>, omnia et in
                        omnibus de quo domnus bone memorie <persName key="#Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#people/2004">Romovald</persName> genitor noster predicti Zacharie
                        abbati concesset, unde et <rs key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma"
                            >precepta potestatis</rs> eius firmata habere videtur, id est in primis
                            <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><rs key="#Houses">casas</rs> cum <rs key="#Curtes">curtes</rs> vel
                                <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables #Agricultural_workers">hortas</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Mills">molino</rs> et valneum, <rs>clausurias</rs></rs> ubi
                        ipsa ecclesia edificata est, et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >terra</rs> vacua qui est trans rivum, et alium <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">hortum</rs> qui esse videtur iuxta fluvio
                            <placeName key="#Rivers #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/2348"
                            >Sabbato</placeName>, qui fuit de quodam <name ref="Trasualdus"
                            >Trasoaldi</name>, simul et <rs key="#Casalia">casa</rs> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/2304" key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property"
                            >Quintodecimo</placeName> qui fuit de quodam <name ref="Pergoaldus"
                            >Pergoaldi</name>, simul cum <rs key="#Fiscal_property"><rs
                                key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineas</rs>,
                            pratis seu <rs>clausurias</rs>, cultum et incultum, omnia et in omnibus
                            de quantum in eodem locis habere visus fuit</rs>, simul et omnem
                        substantiam quod <name ref="Toto Transpadanus">Totuni Transpadano</name>,
                            <rs key="#Fiscal_property"><rs key="#Houses">casas</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineas</rs>,
                            cultum et incultum, movilia atque inmovilia</rs>, qui habitare visus
                        fuit erga <placeName ref="#places/3420"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">Sancto
                            Valentino</placeName>, simul etiam et omnem substantiam qui fuit quodam
                            <name ref="Aloaldus"/>Aloaldi filio quod <name ref="Sidulus"
                            >Siduli</name>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >tam <rs key="#Houses">casas</rs> infra hanc <rs
                                key="#Cities #Fiscal_property">Beneventanam</rs> civitatem quam et
                                <rs key="#Casalia">casalis</rs> et <rs key="#Domuscultae">domu
                                cultas</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineas</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Landed_possessions">territurio</rs>, cultum et incultum,
                            movilia atque inmovilia</rs>, et omnem substantiam quondam <name
                            ref="Fusculus">Fusculi</name>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><rs key="#Cheese #Specialized_workers">casario</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Houses">casas</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineas</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Landed_possessions">territurio</rs>, cultum et incultum,
                            movilia atque inmovilia, <rs key="#Slave">servos et ancillas</rs></rs>,
                        omnia et in omnibus de quantum nominati Fusculi pertinuit substantia, simul
                        etiam et terra in locis qui nominatur **** <placeName ref="#places/2844"
                            key="#Rivers #Fiscal_property">Fluvio Lauro</placeName>, quas cum <name
                            ref="Paulus abbas">Paulo</name> et <name ref="Deusdedit abbas"
                            >Deusdede</name> venerabili <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs> habere visus
                        fuit per domnus Zacharias, seu et substantia qui fuet quoddam <name
                            ref="Iulianus">Iuliani</name>; omnia et in omnibus quantum eius portio
                        fuit , quasm cum Deusdedi abbate habere visus est, simul grege de ***** <rs
                            key="#Sheep #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Specialized_workers"
                            >pecora cum mandras et pascua seu pastores suos</rs> qui fuerunt de
                            <name ref="Corbus">Corbuli</name>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><rs key="#Horses">ammessario tres cum iumentas suas, caballos
                                domitos capita quindecim</rs>, <rs key="#Cows">armentos de baccas et
                                boves domitos</rs>, <rs>carra ferrata [****]</rs>, <rs key="#Silver"
                                >argentum</rs> et <rs key="#Copper">aeramentum</rs></rs> vel omnia
                        de quicquid ipse abbas Zacharias sua spontanea voluntate in ipsum
                        veneravilem locus Beate Sophie offerri previderit, in ea vero ratione ut de
                        hęc omnia in ęcclesia Beate Sophie nostrum preceptum firmavimus eo quod <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions #Privileges #Exemption">ab omni subiugatione
                            hominibus ea absolvimus</rs> ut nęque ab episcopos dominetur nęque a
                        sinodochio defendatur, nęque a nullum monasterium aut a qualibet
                        ęcclesiastico ordine subiugetur, sed <rs key="#Priests">sacerdos</rs> qui in
                        eodem monasterio deservierit, absoluta securitas ei permaneat, <rs
                            key="#Immunity">exceptum ad nostrum sacrum palatium obedientiam
                            habeant</rs>; et qui contra hunc preceptum firmationis atque offertionis
                        ire temptaverit, sicut sacrilegus ab altario repellatur et a trecentorum
                        decem et octo patrum maneat anathemate et cum Iuda traditorem eternum mereat
                        mancipari supplicio, et sic nostra presens definitio atque roburationis
                        preceptum secundum preceptum genituri nostro ex hoc et in perpetuis
                        temporibus maneat roboratus. Quod vero preceptum offertionis seu firmationis
                        ex iussu nominate potestati dictavi ego <persName
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3486">Audefusus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">duddus et referendarius</rs> tibi
                            <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3485">Aldichis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> scribendum. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> in <rs key="#Palatium"
                            >palatio</rs> mense iulio per indictione tertia decima. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
